                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for improving efficiency of carbon dioxide decomposition membrane reactor through industrial hydrogen-containing purge gas",
                    "一种通过工业含氢驰放气提高二氧化碳分解膜反应器效率的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of carbon dioxide conversion and utilization, in particular to a method for improving the efficiency of a carbon dioxide decomposition membrane reactor through industrial hydrogen-containing purge gas. Comprising the following steps: S1, selecting a mixed conductor oxygen permeable membrane as a selective membrane material, and constructing a carbon dioxide decomposition membrane reactor; and S2, introducing the industrial hydrogen-containing purge gas into a carbon dioxide decomposition membrane reactor, adding a low-carbon fuel with a high calorific value into a fuel pipe network, and carrying out a carbon dioxide decomposition reaction. According to the invention, industrial hydrogen-containing purge gas is coupled with the membrane reactor, a traditional methane partial oxidation reaction is replaced, a hydrogen oxidation reaction is carried out, a lower oxygen partial pressure, a larger transmembrane driving force and a larger oxygen removal rate can be provided on a permeation side, the conversion rate of reactants on an oxygen supply side and the efficiency of the membrane reactor are improved, and the production cost is reduced. Meanwhile, dynamics in the carbon dioxide decomposition reaction process is researched, and the oxygen permeation flux in the reaction process can be calculated according to the obtained formula."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及二氧化碳转化利用技术领域，具体为一种通过工业含氢驰放气提高二氧化碳分解膜反应器效率的方法。包括如下步骤：S1：选择混合导体氧渗透膜作为选择性膜材料，构建二氧化碳分解膜反应器；S2：将工业含氢驰放气引入到二氧化碳分解膜反应器中，在燃料管网中加入高热值的低碳燃料，进行二氧化碳分解反应。本发明将工业含氢驰放气与膜反应器耦合，替代传统的甲烷部分氧化反应，而发生氢气氧化反应，在渗透侧可以提供一个更低的氧分压，更大的跨膜驱动力，更大的氧气移出速率，提高了供氧侧反应物的转化率和膜反应器的效率，同时研究了二氧化碳分解反应过程中的动力学，可以根据所得公式计算出反应过程的氧渗透通量。"
                }
            ]
